flowchart TD
    Start((Start)) --> Tx[API transaction inserts outbox event]
    Tx --> Poll[Publisher polls unpublished events]
    Poll --> Publish[Publish to Redpanda]
    Publish --> Mark[Mark published]
    Publish --> Consume[Stream worker consumes]
    Consume --> Validate[Validate and deduplicate]
    Validate --> InsertRaw[Insert raw event to ClickHouse]
    InsertRaw --> Aggregate[Update analytics tables/views]
    Aggregate --> Commit[Commit broker offset]
    Commit --> End((End))
